  "article": "In a groundbreaking announcement, Apple has revealed plans to open a new manufacturing facility in Houston, Texas, where the company will produce its popular Mac Mini desktop computer. This strategic move is set to have far-reaching implications for Apple's supply chain and the broader tech industry.

