  "article": "In a dramatic escalation of the ongoing debate over online safety regulation in the UK, Keir Starmer, the leader of the Labour Party, is facing fierce criticism from prominent campaigners who accuse him of 'appeasing' big tech firms at the expense of robust protections for internet users.

