\"At first, we couldn't believe our eyes,\" said lead archaeologist Dr. Emily Watkins. \"This fossil has an unmistakable resemblance to a human smile, with distinct 'teeth' and 'lips' visible. It's an incredibly unique and perplexing discovery.\"

