  "article": "In a groundbreaking development, a team of engineers has unveiled a revolutionary technology that transforms two-dimensional tile patterns into three-dimensional structures with the simple pull of a string. This innovative approach, which challenges traditional construction methods, has the potential to reshape the way we design and build our environments.

