  "meta_description": "DJI, the world's largest drone maker, has filed a lawsuit against the FCC for 'carelessly' restricting its drone technology.",
  "summary_30w": "DJI, the world's leading drone manufacturer, has filed a lawsuit against the FCC over new regulations that it claims 'carelessly' restrict its drone technology.",
  "article": "In a move that has sent shockwaves through the drone industry, DJI, the world's largest drone maker, has filed a lawsuit against the Federal Communications Commission (FCC) over new regulations that the company claims 'carelessly' restrict its drone technology.

