  "seo_title": "Panasonic Exits TV Manufacturing: The End of an Era",
  "meta_description": "Panasonic, once a leader in plasma TV technology, announces it will no longer manufacture its own televisions, marking the end of an iconic brand's TV production.",
  "summary_30w": "Panasonic, a pioneer in plasma TV technology, has announced it will cease manufacturing its own televisions, signaling the end of an era for the Japanese electronics giant.",
  "article": "Panasonic, the former plasma TV king, has announced that it will no longer manufacture its own televisions, marking a significant shift in the company's strategy. This decision comes as the global TV market continues to evolve, with LCD and OLED technologies taking center stage.

