  "article": "The United Nations Integrated Transition Assistance Mission in Sudan (UNITAMS) has found that the recent siege of the city of El Fasher by the Rapid Support Forces (RSF) militia bears the 'hallmarks of genocide', according to a statement released on Wednesday.

