  "summary_30w": "Caribbean nations demand de-escalation and dialogue as the US imposes a new oil embargo on Cuba, heightening regional tensions.",
  "article": "In a move that has sparked concerns across the Caribbean, the United States has announced a new oil embargo on Cuba, further tightening economic sanctions on the island nation. This decision has drawn sharp criticism from Caribbean leaders, who are now calling for 'de-escalation and dialogue' to resolve the escalating tensions.

