  "meta_description": "Thousands of victims of human trafficking and forced labor in Southeast Asia's cybercrime operations struggle to rebuild their lives amid lack of support.",
  "summary_30w": "Victims of Southeast Asia's booming cybercrime industry face destitution and lack of aid, sparking an international crisis that demands urgent action.",
  "article": "The sprawling cybercrime operations across Southeast Asia have left a devastating trail of human suffering in their wake. Thousands of destitute survivors, many of them victims of human trafficking and forced labor, now find themselves abandoned and struggling to rebuild their lives with little to no support.

