  "article": "In a groundbreaking development, Nissan's latest crossover model has shattered expectations by achieving an astounding 50 miles per gallon in real-world driving conditions. This remarkable feat is thanks to the automaker's innovative E-Power hybrid system, which is poised to redefine the standards of fuel efficiency in the crossover segment.

