  "article": "The Earth's magnetic field is a crucial shield that protects our planet from the harmful effects of solar radiation and cosmic particles. Now, a groundbreaking new space mission, dubbed the 'Space Umbrella Project,' is set to provide unprecedented insights into this vital protective layer.

